  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Reinforcing proper record keeping towards transparency and better service to the members</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&lt;p&gt;1. the project is designed to improve financial reporting  business development  contribution to milk quality improvement for the dairy farmers who supply milk to the leading industry in Rwanda Inyange.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;2. indicators include having the business plan developed   and accounting software made available with reliable financial reports provided.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;3. The sustainability is ensured through cost share  the cooperative seems to be realistic as they agreed to undertake few priority activities which they can successfully ensure financial contribution and ensure future use and benefit the farmers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&apos;margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:0in;font-size:12px;font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot; sans-serif;text-align:justify;&apos;&gt;4. activities aimed to ensure financial management  environmental sustainability are&amp;nbsp;will be executed&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&apos;margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:0in;font-size:12px;font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot; sans-serif;text-align:justify;&apos;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&apos;margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:0in;font-size:12px;font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot; sans-serif;text-align:justify;&apos;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&apos;margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:6.0pt;margin-left:0in;font-size:12px;font-family:&quot;Century Gothic&quot; sans-serif;text-align:justify;&apos;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&lt;p&gt;Rwimbogo dairy cooperative was established in 2008. The cooperative had 60 members that time but got legally registered in 2012 and currently the membership base increased up to 286 with 253 men and 23 women.The assessment team appreciated the good good organization of the cooperative  which is shown by the progress made by the cooperative since establishment up to now. &amp;nbsp;It was also &amp;nbsp;advised that the &amp;nbsp;cooperative should &amp;nbsp;improve its business record keeping system  develop a strategy to diversify income  &amp;nbsp;increase milk production by expanding its animal feeds business  to improve milk quality  ensure extension services reach to all members and on time.&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&lt;p&gt;The goal of this project is to develop &amp;nbsp;a business plan for the animal drugs Pharmacy business  improving milk quality and increasing milk production   and ensure proper financial reporting system is put in place and used for future transparency and accountability.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
  </description>
